{
  "texts": [
    "An alternative to accessing Ground Truth, the IMPACT group offers its own Ground Truth repository (https://www.digitisation.eu/resources/impact-dataset/).",
    "To upload individual ground truth, one must contact the IMPACT centers.Journal of Data Mining and Digital Humanities",
    "The shown screenshot is of particular interest as an example of data reuse: The transcription was done within one project by several student assistants under the direction of a Digital Humanities expert and the project head.Due to the open publication of the data set (as TEI XML) alongside the images by the archives.",
    "Another, independent research group ran a text-to-image process that resulted in an annotated data set suitable for training an ATR model.",
    "This further processing was only possible because of the initial publication of the open TEI XML data set."
  ]
}